rComments: I had her in my first year and she was one of my favourite profs. Very good and straightforward. I'd take any of her classes in a heartbeat!

Professor Ciocani is a great lecturer who was able to make the vast material clear and resonant, as well as cohesive. She cares about her students and gives everyone an opportunity to succeed, as long as they are willing to do the work and put in the effort. Overall, I'd recommend her courses to anyone.

I absolutely adored this class with Professor Ciocani. Her lectures read like a story. Everything I needed to study from I got from her power points and my in class notes. I recommend going to class as much as possible. I didn't read any of the book and received an A- in the class.

She's a super sweet prof, and wants to see you succeed. Her lectures are kinda incomprehensible and very difficult to pay attention to, but if you read and understand the textbook you will do well in the course.
Great teacher, very helpful, kind and answers all your questions. Adds extra, interesting information to lectures. Do take her classes.
